&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;k27bkk&quot; data-start=&quot;4185&quot; data-end=&quot;4250&quot;&gt;Join a fast-growing company in a complex, high-value industry&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;lctd1s&quot; data-start=&quot;4251&quot; data-end=&quot;4326&quot;&gt;Work closely with Product and Engineering on cutting-edge IoT solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1wn0qoe&quot; data-start=&quot;4327&quot; data-end=&quot;4398&quot;&gt;Be a key driver of how we win deals and differentiate in the market&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1i79yq0&quot; data-start=&quot;4399&quot; data-end=&quot;4469&quot;&gt;High visibility and impact across Sales, Marketing, and Leadership&lt;/li&gt;
